 "title": "Braai pie – so delicious over the coals",
 "excerpt": "The braai pie has no set quantities – except for the dough. It's delicious as a side dish or as a starter. Guests are usually amazed when you make it over the coals. You'll need a deep-ish toasting grid. The filling is up to your taste. I'm going to put together two variations. NEEDED: First Filling: …",
